let formula = Foo.degToRad(rad);
`}</code></pre>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "concept"
    }}>{`Concept`}</h2>
    <p>{`When converting from radians to degrees, we must implement the following function:`}</p>
    <p><inlineCode parentName="p">{`œÄ rad = 180 degrees`}</inlineCode></p>
    <p>{`NOTE: In the equation above, `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`œÄ`}</inlineCode>{` is the symbol for `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`pi (3.141592...)`}</inlineCode>{`, and `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`rad`}</inlineCode>{` stands for `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`radians`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
    <p>{`In our Mathium code, it's important to note the following:`}</p>
